{"title":"蓑衣","authors":["聂作平"],"dates":[{"year":1993,"month":12,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓑衣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"聂作平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反披在父亲身上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天就又将敲门"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"透过低矮的山墙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柳条与山歌，杏花和"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笛声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正围绕日渐高远的流云"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而手把犁铧的父亲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎样凑近一袋旱烟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"计算秋后的收成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓑衣，背负整个季节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风侵雨袭，早出晚归"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓑衣永远沉默"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如同多年以后"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那道源自家园和粮食的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每逢春雨炸响屋顶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我和兄弟，仰望蓑衣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一种幸福的刺痛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们热血沸腾"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}